# Snake Game

## Features
- Canvas-based snake game with responsive movement
- Day-night cycle and moon phases based on snake growth
- Multiple fruit types, dynamic soundtrack, sound effects
- High score tracking, modern UI, responsive design
- Auto-collision avoidance and tail-cutting survival mechanics

## Directories & Files

### Root
- **index.html**: Main HTML file loading all game assets
- **README.md**: Documentation and instructions
- **TODO.md**: Task list for ongoing development

### css/
- **styles.css**: UI styling and animations

### img/
- **favicon.svg**: Vector version of the snake head favicon
- **favicon.ico**: ICO version for older browsers
- **favicon-32x32.png**: 32x32 PNG version for various devices
- **apple-touch-icon.png**: Default Apple Touch Icon (180x180)
- **apple-touch-icon-180x180.png**: iPhone 6+/7+/8+/X/XS/11/12/13 devices
- **apple-touch-icon-167x167.png**: iPad Pro
- **apple-touch-icon-152x152.png**: iPad, iPad mini

### js/
- **Game.js**: Main game logic and initialization
- **Snake.js**: Movement and collision detection
- **FoodManager.js**: Food generation and collection
- **GameStateManager.js**: Game state handling
- **GameLoop.js**: Game timing and frame updates
- **GameDrawer.js**: Base drawing utilities
- **SnakeDrawer.js**: Snake rendering with effects
- **SceneDrawer.js**: Background environment
- **MoonDrawer.js**: Moon phases animations
- **Fruits.js**: Fruit types and properties
- **UIManager.js**: UI elements and interactions
- **SoundManager.js**: Sound effect generation
- **MusicManager.js**: Background music playback
- **MusicUtils.js**: Music utility functions
- **MusicSheets.js**: Game melody sequences 